@startuml
title <font size=10>Owner - Riwayat Transaksi</font>

actor Owner
participant "View\nRiwayat Transaksi" as View
participant "Controller" as Ctrl
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Activity Log\nService" as ALS

== VIEW TRANSACTION HISTORY ==
Owner -> View: Buka halaman riwayat transaksi\ndengan filter tanggal & user
View -> Ctrl: GET /owner/riwayat-transaksi
Ctrl -> DB: Query transaksi\ndengan filter
DB --> Ctrl: Kirim semua transaksi
Ctrl --> View: Tampilkan tabel transaksi\ndengan total keseluruhan

== EDIT TRANSACTION ==
Owner -> View: Klik tombol Edit
View -> Ctrl: GET /owner/riwayat-transaksi/{id}/edit
Ctrl -> DB: Load detail transaksi & barang
DB --> Ctrl: Kirim data transaksi
Ctrl --> View: Tampilkan form edit\ndengan item dan qty

Owner -> View: Ubah jumlah items & submit
View -> Ctrl: POST /owner/riwayat-transaksi/{id}/update
Ctrl -> DB: Mulai transaction
Ctrl -> DB: Validate stok & hitung delta qty
DB --> Ctrl: Stok valid
Ctrl -> DB: Update jumlah & subtotal\ndi detail_transaksi
Ctrl -> DB: Adjust stok barang\n(increment/decrement)
Ctrl -> DB: Update total_harga transaksi
Ctrl -> ALS: Log perubahan ke activity_log
ALS -> DB: Insert activity log
Ctrl -> DB: Commit transaction
Ctrl --> View: Redirect ke invoice\ndengan success message

== DELETE TRANSACTION ==
Owner -> View: Klik tombol Delete
View -> Ctrl: GET /owner/riwayat-transaksi/{id}/destroy
Ctrl -> DB: Mulai transaction
Ctrl -> DB: Loop semua detail transaksi
DB --> Ctrl: Kirim detail items
Ctrl -> DB: Refund stok untuk\nsetiap item (increment)
Ctrl -> DB: Hapus detail_transaksi
Ctrl -> DB: Hapus transaksi
Ctrl -> ALS: Log penghapusan\nke activity_log
ALS -> DB: Insert activity log
Ctrl -> DB: Commit transaction
Ctrl --> View: Redirect ke index\ndengan success message
View --> Owner: Tampilkan notifikasi sukses

@enduml
